 T1. All these magnetic features are exactly captured in T and\nH-dependent dielectric constant, epsilon(T) and epsilon(H). This demonstrates\ndirect magnetodielectric coupling in this designed hybrid and yields a new path\nto tune multiferroic ordering and magnetodielectric coupling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 May 2019 21:50:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-20"}
